node.text: I am absolutely loving all of these Fall pieces from @eloquii ! Eloquii has partnered up with @walmartfashion to provide us with affordable fashion pieces under $50 sizes 14-28! Eloquii elements will be sold on Eloquii.com, and Walmart.com! They have pieces for every occasion such as errands, PTA meetings, or just stay cute and comfy for your zoom meetings. Which one was your favorite? #ad #eloquiielements Shop Here: http://liketk.it/2Wgo0 and link of my bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Denise Mercedes 🇩🇴 on July 30, 2021 tagging @targetstyle, and @target. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: #IChoose to try! Before the pandemic, I traveled a lot. During the Pandemic, my mental health was shattered. I have dealt with anxiety for years but the lockdown made it worse. I didn’t want to go anywhere and only stayed at home. Now that I am trying to get back to my usual life (which isn't easy btw), I’m trying to start my journey with traveling again. As a baby step, my friends and I rented a house up in the mountains; next time, I hope it is an even further destination. Don’t be afraid to step out of your comfort zone! Entire look from @targetstyle #ad

Photo shared by Denise Mercedes 🇩🇴 on July 28, 2021 tagging @targetstyle, and @target. May be an image of 1 person, standing, outdoors and brick wall.

node.text: #IChoose to surround myself with positive people. 2020 was hard for many of us and because of this, I have not been able to be around friends and family as much. This has definitely impacted my social anxiety but, little by little we learn to adjust back to our normal lives. Today, I am meeting up with some friends that I have not seen in a while and I am so glad to be reconnecting with positive vibes again. Surround yourself with people who make you happy. Entire look from @targetstyle ! #ad
